GCC has implementation support for such usage, although it did not when cmcstl2 was first implemented. Given that the issue is still open and doesn't yet have wording in the Concepts WP ([n4641](http://wg21.link/n4641) these days), I think it may be to soon to yank these from cmcstl2 after all.

